{"tid":1354028,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"拋磚引玉: 低成本刺蝟自衛戰術","createTime":"2019-07-23T05:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T10:03:01.000Z","uid":37058,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"06ed3545fe45483c25b7fdefcea09ff2e01def1b","tid":1354028,"uid":37058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:17:30.000Z","msg":"相信大家經過元朗事件，都感到<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自我組織防衛力量</span></span>既必要性。我係到嘗試整合下基本常用既長矛陣，結合幾次運動既特性，睇下大家有冇用。希望<span style=\"color: red;\">最底限度</span>，可以<span style=\"color: red;\">減少物理性既傷害</span>。<br />\n<br />\n特點:<br />\n1.低成本<br />\n2.訓練度要求唔高 <br />\n3.隨身物品可以組合 <br />\n4.人數<br />\n<br />\n登登登!我想講既，就係結合大家都好易買到、本身已經有既長傘同埋背囊，形成槍盾陣。槍唔洗多講，盾就如圖示。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4CZVYYc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4CZVYYc.png&h=19cdd2f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無錯，只要本身個袋有足夠多既毛巾，OR硬板，OR毛巾加硬版既結合，再用你既<span style=\"color: red;\">左手掛住呢隻背囊</span>，就可以<span style=\"color: red;\">擔當一個臨時性既盾</span>。不論係和理非亦或勇武既你，面對無差別攻擊既時候，起碼可以擋住走。當日睇到好多人係站內，以及車廂既時候 ，除左開傘，似乎都唔係好擋到攻擊，呢種盾一人一手，保自己保前面既人，行走既時候拼起就係一面盾牆。<br />\n<br />\n好啦，大家知盾點黎，可以進入下一步，就係<span style=\"color: red;\">槍盾結合</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YSHkqDE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYSHkqDE.png&h=ab2c73f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基本原理係，分A，B，C，三層人，A係最外層形成防線，記住A既槍唔係用黎攻擊，而係利用槍身制造足夠既援衝空間，比企係身後既BC兩層槍手去吉突入A槍範圍既人。具體黎講，當A係外圍企好之後，B將自己既槍搭係A既肩頭，平指，作為第二層防線，以及反擊，第三層人側係兩層既空隙之間，不斷突刺，將攻陣既人殺傷 ，每後一層既人都係用黎支援前一層。長槍兵、陣係歷史上長盛不衰，係因為就算係 平民，只要拎起長槍，<span style=\"color: red;\">人數加槍既距離就足以成為巨大既勇氣</span>，對抗敵人既進攻，唔會一擊即散，係最懷情況下<span style=\"color: red;\">保護自己</span>殺傷敵人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JyAJ7Wn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJyAJ7Wn.png&h=40905a43&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ALuiWPH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FALuiWPH.png&h=9730d957&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對警黑勾結 可以保護自己既就只有自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地攞住支水都會比黑警屈做攻擊性武器 而攞住鐵通木棍既恐怖分子就可以同黑警拍拍膊頭互相加油 唔好妄想搵黑警仲會有用 自己人自己保護<br />\n以上只係轉貼友人既戰術分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊討論下打機既攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806ff647df5aca64673663a01ec6bd90ecf2adbe","tid":1354028,"uid":37058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10bd7ad307bf7de70321be0cfc1ad020dc308b70","tid":1354028,"uid":37058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b77356aa9796df65df6d687688bd3b088b3c538","tid":1354028,"uid":1297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:20:51.000Z","msg":"戰術po必推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce371a5b4b1aa791b0ac8c4e0c81b25bf2c8c077","tid":1354028,"uid":37058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:26:11.000Z","msg":"大家一齊討論下可唔可行 保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023776f0932121b0d5db5eff963b1998a337a864","tid":1354028,"uid":37058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05: